    "description": "A synthetic post-harvest fungicide applied to citrus fruit peels to prevent mold growth during transport and storage. Works similarly to E230 but is chemically different (has an -OH group). More effective against certain fungi than biphenyl. Also used as a disinfectant and antiseptic in non-food applications. Should be washed off before using citrus zest in cooking."
  },
